<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	修戒之目的和我们受戒后的努力方向
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%" align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">讲话摘要)</span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%" align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">中国道协副会长　　傅元天</span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">各位戒子：<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">借此法坛，我宣讲一下道士出家之目的和我们受戒后的努力方向，与大众共同商讨。一、人有三品<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一)上品之人，就是经中所称的&ldquo;上士&rdquo;。这种人天性善良，道根深厚，不教自知。对社会共同的秩序、规范自觉地去遵守，好的事情自觉地去做，所谓&ldquo;诸恶莫作，众善奉行&rdquo;。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>　　<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二)中品之人，就是经中所称的&ldquo;中士&rdquo;。这类人与道有缘，自具善根，但不脱俗念，常存烦脑妄想。这种人在道可以修持成仙，在俗亦可以立功、立德、立言。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></div>
<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三)下品之人，就是经中所称的&ldquo;下士&rdquo;。这类人的最大弱点:是非反复，自私自利，一心为已。但其若断然悔悟，在俗仍可以为社会做出贡献，<span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">在道则可以修持延年。</span></span></p>
<span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二、道士称谓<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">古时所谓道士，有三种人可以称之：<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一<span lang="EN-US">)</span>泛称有道之士<span lang="EN-US">(</span>见《春秋繁露》<span lang="EN-US">)</span>。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二<span lang="EN-US">)</span>崇奉道教之人称为道士<span lang="EN-US">(</span>见《黄帝内经》<span lang="EN-US">)</span>。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三<span lang="EN-US">)</span>方士亦称为道士<span lang="EN-US">(</span>见《汉书&middot;王莽传》<span lang="EN-US">)</span>。古代称奉道、修道、以及得道和有道术的人。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">道教自古至今，历史悠久，张道陵创教也有近两千年的历史。纵观往古，以鉴今世。我将道士列为五种<span lang="EN-US">:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一<span lang="EN-US">)</span>道士：终身学道修持<span lang="EN-US">J</span>以宫观为家者。这类道士，我们现在许多宫观就有许多典型。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二<span lang="EN-US">)</span>学士：入道钻研经学义理，学识渊博，并以弘扬道教事业作为白己终身职责者。我们道协原老会长，道教近代泰斗陈撄宁先生就属此类学者。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三<span lang="EN-US">)</span>隐士：隐居出俗，不问世事，学道修仙，以性命修持为主要方向，且道德皆深厚者。如陆修静、陶弘景、司马承祯等人皆属之。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">四<span lang="EN-US">)</span>居士：居家修持，奉道积善，建立功德，吃斋诵道者。社会中这一类的人甚多。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">五<span lang="EN-US">)</span>信士：社会名流学者，著书立说，颂扬道教者。此类人社会中也甚多。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三、道士应持戒<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一<span lang="EN-US">)</span>何谓戒<span lang="EN-US">?</span>&ldquo;戒&rdquo;就是禁止的意思，它帮助断绝恶习，舍妄阪真，扶助人的正行善念，使正气得以发扬，邪念不致妄生。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二<span lang="EN-US">)</span>&ldquo;戒&rdquo;如同载人之舟揖。出家修道者，志在超生死。但是道有真传，法有秘授，法应传授给好人。因此，就需要&ldquo;戒&rdquo;，帮助修道者达到性善的境界，修道不受戒，就得不到法的真传，法得不到传授就好似盲人夜行，终不能得到道的要诀，因此道士出家要持戒。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三<span lang="EN-US">)</span>受戒是出家道士严肃修持的开始。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">四<span lang="EN-US">)</span>戒条是太上之玄意，戒子受戒后要作为自己的行为准则，自觉去遵守。四、道士持戒后，应更好地爱国爱教<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">（一<span lang="EN-US">)</span>自古至今，没有不爱祖国、不孝父母、不敬师长、不讲社会道法的神仙，<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二<span lang="EN-US">)</span>没有共产党就没有新中国，祖国也不可能这样繁荣富强，人民也不可能这样丰衣足食，社会也不可能有这样的安定团结。对道教界来说，也就没有新中国道教，更谈不上今天在白云观传戒和受戒。因此，我们道教界人士应更加热爱社会主义国家，坚决拥护共产党的领导，严格遵循党和政府的政策法令，努力作中华人民共和国的模范公民。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三<span lang="EN-US">)</span>得戒弟子，回到各地宫观，每做一件事，都要用太上之律条来很好地衡量，也都要对国家对人民有益，对社会自觉负责。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">五、遵纪守法<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">（一<span lang="EN-US">)</span>受戒后的弟子，要更加热爱我们的社会主义制度，拥护共产党的领导，<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二<span lang="EN-US">)</span>受戒弟子，已知道太上之律条，必当遵依去做，而不能有戒不守，明知故犯，所谓不知不罪，若知而违者，罪孽深重。　　　<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三<span lang="EN-US">)</span>若受戒弟子，受戒后犯规，涉及的是戒条范围，将按戒规去处置，若涉及国法刑典，也将受到国家法律的处置。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">四<span lang="EN-US">)</span>凡违道规戒律违犯国法者，均要收回其戒牌，并将通报全国宫观，以正视听。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">六、宫观管理<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一<span lang="EN-US">)</span>弟子得戒，只表示有缘得闻太上律条，鞭策和规范自己，今后更好地修持，但对其在原宫观的地位等方而不表示提高或降低之含意。原来在宫观负责什么工作，不因为受戒后就有提高，受戒与在宫观之职务，并非一件事。有的道友修持长进快，有的工作能力强<span lang="EN-US">.</span>各有职责。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二<span lang="EN-US">)</span>得戒弟子，回原宫观后，要更好地配合负责道一长处理好宫观的教务，支持负责道长的宫观工作。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三<span lang="EN-US">)</span>得戒弟子，回宫观后的言行举止教务活动中都要为宫观道众做好的表率。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">(</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">四<span lang="EN-US">)</span>得成弟子，应更加勇猛梢迸，勤修不怠，正己度人，造福社会。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">在职务上，我是中国道教协会副会长，但我和大家一样有缘为同坛戒子，从受戒之日起，我将进一步正心修身，努力做好表率，为道教事业奉献全部精力。谢谢各位。</span></p>
</span></span>
